data.description: Step into the warmth of 347 Lanier Dr, a delightful 2-bed, 1-bath cottage-style home in Madison, Tennessee. The recently renovated bathroom exudes modern charm, complementing the overall cozy feel of the home with beautiful wood paneling and hardwood floors throughout. Outside, a spacious fenced-in backyard with a handy storage shed and garden awaits, offering a private retreat just 15 minutes from Downtown Nashville. Nestled in a serene neighborhood, this well-maintained home captures the essence of suburban comfort with easy access to the city. Make 347 Lanier Dr your home today, where peaceful living meets urban convenience.
